<a href="https://www.goodreads.com/book/show/2372.The_Path_Between_the_Seas"><img alt="The Path Between the Seas: The Creation of the Panama Canal, 1870-1914" src="https://i.gr-assets.com/images/S/compressed.photo.goodreads.com/books/1388197198l/2372._SX98_.jpg" />
